Vertical slices land here, one per capability, when extracted from
hecate-daemon's `apps/guide_mpong_game_lifecycle/src/*'. See README
"Status of the extraction" for the full list.

Each slice is its own OTP app with its own supervisor under `src/`,
matching the daemon's existing layout. The service-level supervisor
(`hecate_mpong_bot_sup`) only owns service-wide infrastructure
(HTTP + mesh RPC); it does NOT supervise slice workers directly.
